reviewText: Shipped out quickly.  Great television series, love it!!
I've never been disappointed with any of my ever-growing Trouble With Father Collection. A remarkably fun, family-themed sitcom from the days when television was actually worth watching.
This was a really funny show from the 50's with Stu Erwin as the father and principal of the high school and his family.  Highly recommend the seller and would definitely buy from again.
I love the stu erwin dvds good condition looking forward to vol 8  and 9 when available
